HOBBYIST SAFE HARBOR

To support the maker community, individual hobbyists may distribute this
software in pre-assembled hardware products WITHOUT a Commercial License,
provided ALL of the following conditions are met:

  1. You are an individual person, not a company or business entity
  2. Total units distributed do not exceed 100 per calendar year
  3. You publish the full source code of your version under GPL v3
  4. You include a visible link to the original repository:
     https://github.com/mp-se/gravitymon
  5. All original copyright notices remain intact in source and UI

  Exceeding any of these conditions voids this exception and requires
  a Commercial License.

